        "remarks": "<format type=\"text/markdown\"><![CDATA[\n## Remarks\n\n`SKColorspacePrimariesCicp` enumerates the color primaries component of CICP (Coding-Independent\nCode Points) as defined in ITU-T H.273. These values correspond to the `ColourPrimaries` field\nof the CICP code and identify the chromaticity coordinates of the color primaries.\n\nUse these values with <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(SkiaSharp.SKColorspacePrimariesCicp,SkiaSharp.SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp)>\nto create a color space from CICP parameters.\n]]></format>",
        "summary": "Specifies the color primaries component of a CICP color space encoding.",
        "remarksRequired": true
      }
    },
